TITLE: Customizing gatsby-plugin-feed in gatsby-config.js
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates customizing the `gatsby-plugin-feed` in `gatsby-config.js` to create a custom RSS feed schema. It includes a GraphQL query to fetch site metadata and Markdown content, and a `serialize` method to format the data for the RSS feed.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/blob/master/docs/docs/how-to/adding-common-features/adding-an-rss-feed.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
