TITLE: Load Google Tag Manager Script with Partytown
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to load the Google Tag Manager (GTM) script using Gatsby's `<Script>` component and the `off-main-thread` strategy, along with initializing the GTM dataLayer.  `process.env.GTM` should be defined in `.env.production` and `.env.development` files. The `forward` prop ensures dataLayer pushes are forwarded to the main thread.
