TITLE: getServerData with GraphQL Query
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to combine `getServerData` with a Gatsby GraphQL page query.  The `data` prop from the GraphQL query is available alongside the `serverData` prop in the React component.  The example fetches a random dog image with `getServerData` and uses a GraphQL query to fetch site metadata.
