TITLE: Adding __typename field in GraphQL queries in Gatsby
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to explicitly add the `__typename` field to GraphQL queries when querying for fields of abstract types (interface or union). In Gatsby v3, `__typename` is no longer added implicitly and must be explicitly included in the query.
