TITLE: Post Template Component
DESCRIPTION: This React component is a template for displaying a single post fetched from Prismic.  It receives the post data via props and renders the title and content. The dangerouslySetInnerHTML is used to render the HTML content fetched from Prismic. A GraphQL query is used to fetch the data for a specific post by UID.
