TITLE: Updating Queries for downloadLocal
DESCRIPTION: This GraphQL query demonstrates how to update your queries when using the `downloadLocal` setting. It queries the `localFile` field of a `ContentfulAsset` to access the locally stored file and then uses `childImageSharp` and `gatsbyImageData` to create image data for `gatsby-plugin-image`.
