TITLE: Config Function for DSG based on Post Date
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet configures Deferred Static Generation (DSG) based on the date of a blog post. It queries all posts older than 2021-10-31 and marks them as deferred. The inner function compares the current slug with the set of old posts to determine if the page should be deferred. Requires `gatsby-transformer-remark`.
