TITLE: Sourcing data using createNode API in gatsby-node.js
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to source data manually using the `sourceNodes` API and `createNode` action in `gatsby-node.js`. It fetches data from the GitHub API and creates a node in Gatsby's data layer.
