TITLE: Agility Page Component (JSX)
DESCRIPTION: This is the `AgilityPage` component, which fetches page and item data from Agility CMS using GraphQL queries based on the page and content IDs. It then renders the page content using the `AgilityPageTemplate` component, passing in the viewModel. This component acts as the master page template.
