TITLE: Configuring gatsby-source-graphql in gatsby-config.js
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code configures the `gatsby-source-graphql` plugin in `gatsby-config.js`. It specifies the type name, field name, and URL of the Gentics Mesh GraphQL API. The `typeName` and `fieldName` determine how the data will be accessed in Gatsby's GraphQL layer.
