TITLE: Conditional Queries with Directives in GraphQL
DESCRIPTION: This GraphQL query shows how to conditionally include or skip parts of a query using the `@include` and `@skip` directives, controlled by variables. It conditionally includes the `date` field based on the `$withDate` variable.  It also includes different fragments and entire queries based on `$preview` variable.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/blob/master/docs/docs/graphql-reference.md#_snippet_29

LANGUAGE: graphql
