TITLE: Configuring tableOfContents in GraphQL query (GraphQL)
DESCRIPTION: A GraphQL query demonstrating how to configure the `tableOfContents` field with `absolute`, `pathToSlugField`, `heading`, and `maxDepth` options. These options customize the generation of the table of contents.
