TITLE: Testing Plugin Options Schema (After) - __tests__/gatsby-node.js
DESCRIPTION: Tests the plugin options schema, but now expects warnings instead of errors for unknown options, reflecting changes in `gatsby-plugin-utils`.  `testPluginOptionsSchema` now returns `warnings`, `isValid` and `hasWarnings`.
