SOURCE: https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/blob/master/docs/docs/how-to/plugins-and-themes/creating-a-transformer-plugin.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
query {
  allFile {
    edges {
      node {
        internal {
          type
          mediaType
          description
          owner
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

