TITLE: Defining Child Relations with types and mimeTypes
DESCRIPTION: This GraphQL snippet demonstrates how to combine the `types` and `mimeTypes` arguments in the `@childOf` extension to define child relations. It adds `childMdx` as a child to `File` nodes and nodes with `@mimeTypes` set to "text/markdown" or "text/x-markdown".
