TITLE: GraphQL Query for Tech Data
DESCRIPTION: This GraphQL query demonstrates how to query the `tech` object via the referred items in `experience` after setting up the node mapping in Gatsby.  This allows you to fetch linked technology data based on the tech IDs in the experience data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/blob/master/docs/docs/reference/config-files/gatsby-config.md#_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
query {
  allExperienceJson {
    edges {
      node {
        company
        position
        from
        to
        items {
          label
          description
          link
          tech {
            label
            color
            icon
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

