TITLE: Format Date in Markdown Remark Query GraphQL
DESCRIPTION: This query retrieves MarkdownRemark nodes and formats the date field. It uses the `formatString` argument within the `date` field to format the date. It also applies a filter to ensure the date is not null.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/blob/master/examples/graphql-reference/content/queries.md#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
{
  allMarkdownRemark(filter: { frontmatter: { date: { ne: null } } }) {
    edges {
      node {
        frontmatter {
          title
          date(formatString: "dddd DD MMMM YYYY")
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

