SOURCE: https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/blob/master/packages/gatsby-source-contentful/README.md#_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
{
  allContentfulBlogPost {
    nodes {
      heroImage {
        gatsbyImageData(layout: FULL_WIDTH)
      }
    }
  }
}
```

