SOURCE: https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/blob/master/docs/docs/reference/release-notes/migrating-from-v2-to-v3.md#_snippet_33

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
exports.onCreateNode = ({ actions, node }) => {
  const { deleteNode } = actions

- deleteNode({ node })
+ deleteNode(node)
}
```

