TITLE: Creating data directory using onPreBootstrap
DESCRIPTION: Creates a data directory within the gatsby-theme-events using the onPreBootstrap lifecycle API.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/blob/master/docs/tutorial/building-a-theme.md#_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
const fs = require("fs")

// Make sure the data directory exists
exports.onPreBootstrap = ({ reporter }) => {
  const contentPath = `${__dirname}/data/`

  if (!fs.existsSync(contentPath)) {
    reporter.info(`creating the ${contentPath} directory`)
    fs.mkdirSync(contentPath)
  }
}
```

