TITLE: JavaScript snippet naming JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: shows an example of snippet naming using comments
SOURCE: https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/blob/master/packages/gatsby-remark-embed-snippet/README.md#_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// start-snippet{funcA}
function factorial(x) {
    if (x <= 1) return 1
    else return x * factorial(x - 1)
}
// end-snippet{funcA}

function display() {
    let x = 5
    // start-snippet{invokeA}
    let xfact = factorial(x)
    // end-snippet{invokeA}
    println!(`{} factorial is {}`, x, xfact)
}
```

