LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
add_action('graphql_register_types', function() {
  register_graphql_field( 'Post', 'testGatsbyField', [
    'type' => 'String',
    'description' => __( 'Test field for demonstration', 'your-textdomain' ),
    'resolve' => function() {
      return 'gatsby test!';
    }
  ]);
});
```

