TITLE: CSS for Line Numbering Only
DESCRIPTION: This CSS configures the style for when only line numbers are used without line highlighting.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/blob/master/packages/gatsby-remark-prismjs/README.md#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: css
CODE:
```
/**
 * If you only want to use line numbering
 */

.gatsby-highlight {
  background-color: #fdf6e3;
  border-radius: 0.3em;
  margin: 0.5em 0;
  padding: 1em;
  overflow: auto;
}

.gatsby-highlight pre[class*="language-"].line-numbers {
  padding: 0;
  padding-left: 2.8em;
  overflow: initial;
}
```

