TITLE: GraphQL query with custom typeName
DESCRIPTION: Example of a GraphQL query using the custom `typeName` configured in the previous snippet.  Shows how to query all YAML nodes using the specified type.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/blob/master/packages/gatsby-transformer-yaml/README.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
{
  allYaml {
    edges {
      node {
        value
      }
    }
  }
}
```
